com.coveros.selenified.element.check

Class AssertEquals

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveros.selenified.element.check.AssertEquals

  • public class AssertEquals
extends Object
    AssertEquals implements Equals to provide some additional assertion capabilities. It will handle all assertions performed on the actual element. These asserts are custom to the framework, and in addition to providing easy object oriented capabilities, they take screenshots with each assertion to provide additional traceability, and assist in troubleshooting and debugging failing tests. Equals checks that elements have a particular value associated to them.
    Version:
    3.2.1
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
